getDistToFinish

public double getDistToFinish()
Get the distance to the finish:
  • On current leg:
    • Using either distance projected onto straigh line between previous and next mark or
    • The distance projected onto the wind vector passing through the next mark
  • On the following legs: The direct distance between the marks

Returns:
the distance to the finish, projected straight onto the wind-direction
